I'm not going to be alone again.

1146
01:31:29,066 --> 01:31:31,736
-[yells]
-[screeches]

1147
01:31:32,820 --> 01:31:34,489
I finally started hoping…

1148
01:31:37,033 --> 01:31:38,868
