1149
01:31:39,660 --> 01:31:41,662
[Red Person hissing]

1150
01:31:43,456 --> 01:31:46,584
I'm not gonna let you
take away my friends!

1151
01:31:50,838 --> 01:31:52,840
[screeching]

1152
01:32:02,683 --> 01:32:04,185
[pole clatters]

1153
01:32:04,769 --> 01:32:06,479
-[sighs]
-[music swells]

1154
