[alarm ringing and vibrating]

1162
01:33:48,998 --> 01:33:52,627
JULY 6, WEDNESDAY

1163
01:33:57,715 --> 01:33:59,717
[rain pouring outside]

1164
01:34:00,926 --> 01:34:02,094
[Asuka sighs]

1165
01:34:20,946 --> 01:34:23,407
[woman] <i>Police were called yesterday</i>
<i>when, during a renovation</i>

1166
01:34:23,491 --> 01:34:26,827
<i>of the chapel at Acacia Academy,</i>
<i>a construction worker</i>

1167
01:34:26,911 --> 01:34:29,455
<i>-discovered a human skull…</i>
-[man] Isn't that your school, Asuka?

1168
01:34:29,538 --> 01:34:30,831
<i>…in a well on the school grounds.</i>

1169
01:34:30,915 --> 01:34:33,834
-Yeah, it is.
